  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0dd0\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc3\u0db1\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dda \u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dda \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0da7\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dd4 \u0d85\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf \u0dc3\u0dd9\u0dc0\u0dd3\u0db8\u0da7 \u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 \u0dc4\u0dbb\u0dc3\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Gasoline crosses over to search for the elephant that crashed into Jackson's car",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The photo of the elephant currently circulating on social media claiming to be the wild elephant that collided with the cab Mr. Jackson Anthony was traveling in is a fake, and the said wild elephant could not be found today (4th) afternoon, North West and Anuradhapura Regions have confirmed. Mr. Chandana Jayasinghe, Senior Veterinarian of Pandulagama Wildlife Office says.",
        "The doctor also said that although the wildlife officials are engaged in searching for the condition of the wild elephant, but due to the lack of fuel, obstacles have arisen in those activities.",
        "The doctor said that a photograph of an injured elephant is currently circulating on social media in connection with this accident, adding that the photograph is a photograph of an elephant in India that had an accident a few years ago.",
        "The patient named Saman Anthony, who is the brother of Mr. Jackson Anthony, who is being treated in this accident, has received treatment in the surgical intensive care unit today (4th) due to the damage to his lungs, and the condition of Iresh Lakmal, who was traveling in the same car, is not serious. Dr. Dulan Samaraweera, Director of Anuradhapura Teaching Hospital, said that he is being treated in a general ward of Anuradhapura Teaching Hospital.",
        "Veteran actor Mr. Jackson Anthony and three persons participated in a filming activity at Hachchikuchi Viharaya located in Giribawa 'Tambutta' area, Galgamuwa, and while they were coming to the shelter in Anuradhapura at around ten o'clock last night (2nd), the cab in which the group was traveling crashed in Talawa Moragoda area. The accident was caused by the collision of an elephant.",
        "Mr. Jackson Anthony, who was injured in that accident, was transferred to the Colombo National Hospital for further treatment that same night."
      ],
